Interface MarketListener


  • public interface MarketListener
    MarketListener is the interface for outbound events from the matching engine.

    • Method Detail

      • match

        void match(long restingOrderId,
           long incomingOrderId,
           long price,
           long executedQuantity,
           long remainingQuantity)
        Match an incoming order to a resting order in the order book. The match occurs at the price of the order in the order book.
        Parameters:
        restingOrderId - the order identifier of the resting order
        incomingOrderId - the order identifier of the incoming order
        price - the execution price
        executedQuantity - the executed quantity
        remainingQuantity - the remaining quantity of the resting order

        side - the side
        price - the limit price
        size - the size

        remainingQuantity - the remaining quantity
